channel.description:
I will be trying to finish this game via LiveStream for the last time today in about 20 minutes.
The game being played is Resident Evil 1: The Remake.
The past 2 times I died, and it froze. So hoping to finish this game this time.
If you have some time to kill this is for you, it is going to be an epic play through.
